{"tid":282820,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓教練：能夠賽和香港這支強隊，已是不錯的成績","createTime":"2017-06-13T16:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T11:07:35.000Z","uid":4361,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"588b8b1044e1f9b59108f0185288486a2029b279","tid":282820,"uid":4361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"周二亞盃外B組，香港足球代表隊在主場以1:1賽和北韓。在末段，更有北韓球員踢到抽筋。北韓主帥安達臣表示，他滿意球隊賽和香港，更讚香港是一支強隊。<br />\n<br />\n北韓教練安達臣賽後指：「比起去年11月，今仗精采得多，香港踢法直接，用很多長波，特別是下半場為我們帶來很多麻煩。上半場我們有點欠運，我們有較多機會，惟沒有入球，更因為後防一個錯誤而失球。能夠賽和香港這支強隊，已是不錯的成績。」他又否認球員體力有問題：「我們一直主攻，而香港只是專注反擊，體力消耗當然較慢。」"},{"pid":"bed43aad20de46ca5d86ffd6db3d499f98908609","tid":282820,"uid":4302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:11:41.000Z","msg":"咁客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5dfe443fc19efacbe2d1cc1a73ecaed5cafd59","tid":282820,"uid":4361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c960ac0fdf445916ac2da61fc5439f5d0f2905e","tid":282820,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8984a5fd80f10664014c833164f6359fc06f3c","tid":282820,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:15:38.000Z","msg":"反kim果班人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e40b9702d71a3e629ff67043337a1e13fe9161b","tid":282820,"uid":15278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T16:15:38.000Z","msg":"香港踢法直接，用很多長波<br />\n<br />\nKim sir戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a640a6cff72e7a6d1f7c9c841d6b6fb6381f365","tid":282820